title: Executive Order 6776-Veterans Regulation No. 8 (a)
content: Executive Order No. 6096, dated March 31, 1933 (Veterans Regulation No. 8), is hereby canceled as of the date thereof.
citation: Franklin D. Roosevelt, Executive Order 6776-Veterans Regulation No. 8 (a) Online by Gerhard Peters and John T. Woolley, The American Presidency Project https://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/node/373478
